{"tid":1689263,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[教學片] 被索帶綁手時如何鬆脫","createTime":"2019-11-02T17:30:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T17:46:45.000Z","uid":336896,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"10303f7cf4b3af912a8a449e04de533f47ad47e1","tid":1689263,"uid":336896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:30:30.000Z","msg":"近來治安唔好，有啲綁匪好鍾意用索帶綁架人<br />\n所以上網搵咗兩段教學<br />\n如果係綁前面，可以抬高雙手，然後一嘢向 hip 位推落去，將佢撞開<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1ZvEXcRE4BU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D1ZvEXcRE4BU&d=5AUjfk%2BhgFT%2FKzSacqcGpC%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=c6a83951\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1ZvEXcRE4BU</a><br />\n<br />\n如果手係綁喺後面，坐低，將雙手由屁股下面繞過去前面。之後用返以上方法，又或者用鞋帶去磨斷佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Gxeq3j0u0hE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGxeq3j0u0hE&d=5AUjfk%2BhgFT%2FKzSacqcGpC%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=6652962a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Gxeq3j0u0hE</a><br />\n<br />\n利申：此方法只係為咗以免被不法綁匪綁架"},{"pid":"666a3c1441f235327ec2a4e7db1dbf62eacd562e","tid":1689263,"uid":336896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:30:47.000Z","msg":"P 牌推唔倒 post ，覺得有用嘅話請幫忙推"},{"pid":"c0583147da0498c05d70544bd39adbdc564b5d21","tid":1689263,"uid":262146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:30:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/daWoJsy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdaWoJsy.png&h=16518c90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oLQwSkW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoLQwSkW.png&h=766c26b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TLR4sUj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTLR4sUj.png&h=1dd0aacc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\